sources.title: SEAL Team VI | Full Movie | Action War Drama
sources.description:
SEAL Team VI - Inspired by actual events: This heroic saga depicts an elite counter-terrorism team's black ops incursion into Iraq four days prior to Operation: Desert Shield and the harrowing consequences its members faced when their covert mission was compromised.
2008.  Stars: Jeremy Davis, Ken Gamble, Zach McGowan
